OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSunny spells
OL,6,Fwith occasional high-level cloud to
OL,7,Fend the day. A clear night for most,
OL,8,Falthough some low cloud may affect the
OL,9,FKent coast. A warm night for the
OL,10,Fmajority of the region.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA bright day with some low
OL,13,Fcloud lingering along the Kent coast
OL,14,Fin the morning. A fresh northeasterly
OL,15,Fwind by the sea. Feeling hot inland,
OL,16,Fcooler along coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
