OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fperiods Saturday morning, brightening
OL,7,Fup by the afternoon. A clear and dry
OL,8,Fstart to Monday, sunshine turning hazy
OL,9,Fby the afternoon, showers possible
OL,10,Fovernight. Cloudy periods on Tuesday.
